ects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/68174/', '', 'Tetracaine, Azelastine, Ketotifen, Desloratadine, Fexofenadine', 'Amisulpride, Pimavanserin', 1767369485);
